{"name":"Hey Buddy","type":"feat","img":"modules/morkborg-3p/images/tokens/soul-damned-drunkard.png","system":{"description":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">You are often overlooked and can surprise enemy if they are moving and you are not by jumping up shouting &ldquo;Brother can you spare the time to die?&rdquo; (or similar catchphrase). </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">DR 12 Agility to surprise in this way before combat rounds begin; if successful you get a free attack. Only works on sentient enemies.</span></p>","rollFormula":"1d20+@abilities.agility.value","rollMacro":"","rollLabel":"Hey!"},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.1ctjNj2kPHpbrkU1"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"morkborg","systemVersion":"2.0.0","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1674920014120,"modifiedTime":1684064002402,"lastModifiedBy":"LYF9zR8SvB0h2e6R"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"ExGbll5H7WY8LROo":3},"_id":"jALR8QRDhrqAGTDJ"}
